So ſaying, he turned away to purſue ſome anatomical preparation, and I ſaw clear enough that we have no ſouls at all. My preſent employ was not congenial to my deſire of benefiting mankind. I was like a gem hid in the mud, and I reſolved to quit my ſituation. Indeed, the houſe-maid had been a little troubleſome, for in teaching her ſome of Munro's anatomical compariſons, we were naturally led from theory to practice, for ſhe had ſo much of the modern ſpirit of inquiry, that ſhe frequently attended diſſections promiſcuouſly with the other ſexOne of the purſuits pointed out to females; 
